Obviously Gura herself, being visually the youngest character in the whole pantheon, has the furthest thing from a large chin.  I get it, of course‚Äîthis isn't a Japanese animation studio and it's all essentially just a simulation of actual anime, really not unlike efforts like Teen Titans or something.   But when a casual scrutiny can surface instances where things could clearly have gone better, then there was room for easy improvement.
